  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tTyping<br />\n\tTyping is entering information on a keyboard. Who is typing? Why is the person typing? What is being typed?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They typed the document... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) university students typing notes in class<br />\n\t2) long nails make it difficult to type<br />\n\t3) a person learning to type on a foreign language keyboard<br />\n\t4) a keyboard is designed so as to minimize stress on the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/joint\" target=\"_blank\">joint</a>s when typing<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWhile Wolfe was busily typing away on his computer, he heard a rush of footsteps and looked up, just as the intern stopped at his desk, breathlessly gasping for air. &ldquo;This is fresh off the press! You have to read it! I've got to go, the editor is waiting for me downstairs,&rdquo; exclaimed the intern before turning to leave. Suddenly, the intern turned around, &ldquo;I'm sure you'll like what you see inside,&rdquo; he said with a wink and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dash\" target=\"_blank\">dash</a>ed off. At the moment, though, Wolfe had no time to spare. The meeting would be in thirty minutes and he needed to finish his work.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162000685074/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721260/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p721260\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724552/\">Quora精选 语言学学士教你背单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p538280/\">致单身者：如何一个人过得精彩</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724524/\">全球审美差异: 什么样才算美男子？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724073/\">Duang~这些年你究竟会不会学新概念？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724655/\">唐顿庄园太火 中国富豪急求英式管家</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724407/\">如何精通多国语言 李光耀的5大学习心得</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724374/\">新加坡国父李光耀去世 享年91岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724630/\">德国载150人客机在法坠毁 无人生还</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723865/\">不知不觉变胖子: 你一天吃了多少糖？</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\