  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/fanli/201304/5959eaa1-3cea-48b1-9ed8-aa6345c5c775.jpg\" style=\"height: 254px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723161\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBut first, a recent BBC <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/survey\" target=\"_blank\">survey</a> identified seven different social classes, including an established middle class. That is a wealthy, large and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/gregarious\" target=\"_blank\">gregarious</a> group, scoring highly on cultural capital. Well, I've got a man sitting right here who thinks that's just completely wrong. David Boyle, at the New Economics Foundation, doesn't see the middle class as wealthy or gregarious. He argues that it's been killed &quot;stone dead&quot; and he's identified the murderer. Just like on the Orient Express, it wasn't one killer, but several, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unaffordable\" target=\"_blank\">unaffordable</a> house prices, greedy banks, the me-first <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/scramble\" target=\"_blank\">scramble</a> for good education, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/extortionate\" target=\"_blank\">extortionate</a> child care costs, and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/plundered\" target=\"_blank\">plundered</a> pensions. All of them took a turn stabbing the knife into the Boden-clad chest of the middle class. Well, David's with me here now. He's carried a bag of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/organic\" target=\"_blank\">organic</a> rice cakes - carefully stashed away, along with Mark Littlewood, director general of the Institute of Economic Affairs, and down the line, we also have the social historian Selina Todd of Oxford University.</p>\n<p>\n\tDavid, in the 1990s, there was a lot of middle class unemployment. In the 70s, middle class savings were being eaten away by inflation. In the 30s, everyone was a lot worried about losing their servants. The middle class has always been under threat.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723161/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p723161\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724552/\">Quora精选 语言学学士教你背单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p538280/\">致单身者：如何一个人过得精彩</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724524/\">全球审美差异: 什么样才算美男子？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724073/\">Duang~这些年你究竟会不会学新概念？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724655/\">唐顿庄园太火 中国富豪急求英式管家</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724407/\">如何精通多国语言 李光耀的5大学习心得</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724374/\">新加坡国父李光耀去世 享年91岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p724630/\">德国载150人客机在法坠毁 无人生还</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p723